{"tid":895145,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼的斷指習俗 失去一個親人就要切掉一節手指頭","createTime":"2018-11-09T03:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T14:00:38.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea76bccc1a4d302e6da58009e13665f8141c5fc5","tid":895145,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"印度尼西亞的一個「Dani tribe」部落。在這裡的女性是主內家務，以男人為中心而活<br />\n不過在這裡有一項相當特別的「斷指習俗」，那就是部落裡如果有人死了，那跟死者關係比較親密的女性親屬就需要砍斷一節手指來以示哀悼。而比較親密的親屬例如像是姐姐妹妹、媽媽、女兒或者奶奶等等關係都算，只要失去一個親人，家裡的女人就要切掉一節手指頭以示哀悼...所以活得越久，身邊的家人比你還早離開，你的手指頭就會越來越短，不過現在因為現在漸漸地有些外來人進入了這個部落，所以部落也漸漸的變成少部分的傳統家庭還在維持這樣的斷指習俗<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/28/88/qZqUo56XkaKZraQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F28%2F88%2FqZqUo56XkaKZraQ.jpg&h=cbe0ef22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/28/88/qZqUo56XkaGZqqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F28%2F88%2FqZqUo56XkaGZqqQ.jpg&h=891d5bd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/28/88/qZqUo56XkaGZqqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F28%2F88%2FqZqUo56XkaGZqqY.jpg&h=5af84064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/28/88/qZqUo56XkaOWqaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F28%2F88%2FqZqUo56XkaOWqaQ.jpg&h=e8452259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/28/88/qZqUo56XkaGZqqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F28%2F88%2FqZqUo56XkaGZqqc.jpg&h=4ef50fd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0050968464cc365f9bbe9db2fb862ffceaaa0385","tid":895145,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T